I truly do not understand the problems people have with this recipe. It's not deceptively simple to make...it IS simple to make. I've made it more than once, and the only change I made this most recent time was to add a little bit of peppermint extract because I'm a huge peppermint fan. They came out chewy and rich and minty, and I really like them. Also, make sure you use non-Dutch-process cocoa powder if you want a really nice, fudgy taste! Follow as written.

